  "text": "Found all Java source files implementing Kafka's consumer group partition assignment strategies in the apache/kafka repository (sg-evals/kafka--0753c489). The implementation includes both eager and cooperative rebalancing protocols.\n\n**Concrete Assignor Implementations:**\n\n1. **RangeAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/RangeAssignor.java) - Extends AbstractPartitionAssignor. Implements range assignment strategy that lays out available partitions in numeric order and consumers in lexicographic order, dividing partitions evenly per topic. Supports rack-aware assignment to align consumer and partition replica racks on a best-effort basis.\n\n2. **RoundRobinAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/RoundRobinAssignor.java) - Extends AbstractPartitionAssignor. Implements round-robin assignment strategy across all available partitions and consumers, providing uniform distribution when all consumer subscriptions are identical. Supports static membership for sticky assignment behavior.\n\n3. **StickyAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/StickyAssignor.java) - Extends AbstractStickyAssignor. Implements sticky assignment using eager rebalancing protocol. Guarantees balanced assignment while preserving existing partition assignments during reassignments, reducing partition movement overhead.\n\n4. **CooperativeStickyAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/CooperativeStickyAssignor.java) - Extends AbstractStickyAssignor. Cooperative version of StickyAssignor that uses cooperative rebalancing protocol instead of eager, allowing for fewer partition revocations during rebalancing. Uses the same sticky assignment logic as StickyAssignor but only revokes partitions being transferred to other consumers.\n\n**Base Classes:**\n\n5. **AbstractPartitionAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/AbstractPartitionAssignor.java) - Abstract base class implementing ConsumerPartitionAssignor interface. Provides common functionality including partition collection, rack-aware assignment logic, and member information management. All assignor implementations extend from this class either directly or through AbstractStickyAssignor.\n\n6. **AbstractStickyAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/AbstractStickyAssignor.java) - Intermediate abstract base class extending AbstractPartitionAssignor. Contains shared sticky assignment implementation used by both StickyAssignor and CooperativeStickyAssignor. Implements rack-aware assignment with partition movement tracking, supporting both eager and cooperative rebalancing protocols."
}

